    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "im kinda frustrated because my doctor is out of town and i cant wait days for a callback just for a tension headache. everyone says ibuprofen is the standard for this. if i just stick to a low dose like 200mg, isn't that practically harmless for someone with stable CKD? it seems like a huge stretch to say a single pill is going to cause immediate damage.",
